Package: libccsp-common
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: CCSP Common Library
 RDK Central Common CCSP Component (Common Component Software Platform) library
 providing core functionality for CCSP components including message bus integration,
 debug API, utilities, and COSA (Component Object System Architecture) support.
 .
 This package contains the runtime libraries.

